OL,3,C'Shocking' chaos at HMP Wandsworth was
OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHMIP issued an Urgent Notification in
OL,8,FMay after a "catastrophic inspection"
OL,9,Ffound alarmingly high rates of self-
OL,10,Fharm, dangerous levels of violence and
OL,11,Fnearly 50% of prisoners taking drugs.
OL,13,FThe report concluded that HMP
OL,14,FWandsworth was "not safe" and 10 self-
OL,15,Finflicted deaths had occurred since
OL,16,Fthe last inspection, with a "high and
OL,17,Frising" rate of self-harm.
