OL,3,C'Shocking' chaos at HMP Wandsworth was
OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAround three quarters of men reported
OL,8,Fspending more than 22 hours a day in
OL,9,F"appalling conditions" in their cells,
OL,10,Fthe report noted.
OL,12,FInspectors carrying out two random
OL,13,Froll checks were unable to verify this
OL,14,Fbecause "record keeping was so poor",
OL,15,Fwith staff unable to account for where
OL,16,Fprisoners on their wings were.
OL,18,FThe report also found that more than
OL,19,Fhalf of men said it was easy to get
OL,20,Fdrugs and the smell of cannabis was
OL,21,F"ubiquitous".
