OL,3,C'Shocking' chaos at HMP Wandsworth was
OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"The prison population crisis has
OL,8,Fundoubtedly compounded the pressures
OL,9,Fon the jail, but the appalling
OL,10,Fconditions at Wandsworth did not
OL,11,Fappear overnight and are the result of
OL,12,Fsustained decline permitted to happen
OL,13,Fin plain view of leaders in the jail,
OL,14,FHM Prison & Probation Service (HMPPS)
OL,15,Fand the MoJ whose own systems clearly
OL,16,Fidentified the prison as struggling."
OL,18,FMr Taylor added: "There was a degree
OL,19,Fof despondency amongst prisoners at
OL,20,FWandsworth that I have not come across
OL,21,Fin my time as Chief Inspector.
