OL,3,C'Shocking' chaos at HMP Wandsworth was
OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Many well-meaning and hard-working
OL,8,Fleaders and staff persevered at
OL,9,FWandsworth, but they were often
OL,10,Ffighting against a tide of cross-
OL,11,Fcutting, intractable problems that
OL,12,Frequire comprehensive, long-term
OL,13,Fsolutions.
OL,15,F"For this troubled prison to begin to
OL,16,Frecover, Wandsworth needs permanent
OL,17,Fexperienced leaders at all levels who
OL,18,Fare invested in the long-term future
OL,19,Fof the prison to improve security,
OL,20,Fsafety and guide their less
OL,21,Fexperienced colleagues."
