OL,3,C'Shocking' chaos at HMP Wandsworth was
OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FPia Sinha, chief executive of the
OL,8,FPrison Reform Trust, said HMP
OL,9,FWandsworth was "emblematic of a system
OL,10,Fthat has been running on fumes for
OL,11,Fmany years, through our overuse of
OL,12,Fprison and chronic underinvestment in
OL,13,Fthe prisons estate".
OL,15,FThe chief executive of the social
OL,16,Fjustice charity Nacro, Campbell Robb,
OL,17,Fsaid the report highlighted alarming
OL,18,Ffailings "from dangerous levels of
OL,19,Fovercrowding, to soaring rates of
OL,20,Fviolence and squalid conditions
OL,21,Freminiscent of a Victorian workhouse".
